IAM - Password Policy
    Have users make strong passwords
    Use Multifactor Authentication
    1 - Virtual MFA Device - Google Aauthenticator or Authy
    2 - Universal 2nd Factor (U2f) Security Key - YubiKey
    3 - Hardware Key Fob MFA Device - Gemalto 
    4 - Hardware Key Fob MFA Device for AWS GovCloud - SurePassID

IAM - Roles for Services
    Help with assigning permissions

IAM - Security Tools 
    Credentials Report (account-level) - lists all your account's users and status 
    Access Advisor (user-level) - Access advisor shows the service permissions
    